metadata.name: Astronaut sitting on the rock
metadata.description:
Space and its galaxies, its planets of the solar system, the interstellar cosmos, an infinite and unknown universe that our NASA astronauts are trying to understand through exploration. The rockets cross the skies to discover new stars and why not new extraterrestrial civilizations. Perhaps they will come across flying saucers, small aliens or gigantic extraterrestrials !

MEDIUM: Digital 2d Art || YEAR: 2021 || DIMENSIONS: 5820*8120px (base x height) || DEPTH: 300ppi
